    "Desktop is also divided into 3DOF and 6DOF.",
    "The first one includes obsolete devices, such as eMagine Z800, Fove 0, nVisor and Oculus Rift DK1.",
    "In contrast, 6DOF offers higher immersion levels and sense of presence, which are especially important nowadays to develop interactive experiences with more quality (Rossi et al. 2021).",
